*   `autoSizeText()`, `getAutoSizeMaxTextSize()`, `getAutoSizeMinTextSize()`, `getAutoSizeStepGranularity()`, `getAutoSizeTextAvailableSizes()`, `getAutoSizeTextType()`, `isAutoSizeEnabled()`: These methods are all direct delegates to the `mAutoSizeTextHelper` for managing text auto-sizing features.
