*   `loadFromAttributes(@Nullable AttributeSet r24, int r25)`: This is the primary entry point for initializing the helper from XML attributes.
    *   It uses `TintTypedArray.obtainStyledAttributes` to read `AppCompatTextHelper` specific attributes, including resource IDs for compound drawables (left, top, right, bottom, start, end).
